            "id": 6404932,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 埃克森美孚(XOM-US)大跌5.03%，報161.13美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>埃克森美孚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:XOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/XOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">XOM-US</a>)截至台北時間01日22:17股價下跌8.53美元，報161.13美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量7,883,772（股），盤中最高價168.00美元、最低價161.10美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.67%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.77%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+3.14%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>埃克森美孚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:XOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/XOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">XOM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.59%</li> <li>近 1 月：+11.25%</li> <li>近 3 月：+40.98%</li> <li>近 6 月：+50.47%</li> <li>今年以來：+40.98%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6404932",
